{
  "vuln_id": "tomcat_cve2017_12615",
  "dispatch_skill": "tomcat_exploit",
  "description": "Apache Tomcat 8.5.19 版本中，由于web.xml配置readonly=false，允许通过PUT方法上传文件，结合路径后缀绕过（如添加/）可上传JSP webshell，导致远程代码执行。",
  "category": "file_upload",
  "cves": [
    "CVE-2017-12615"
  ],
  "match_keywords": [
    "Tomcat",
    "CVE-2017-12615",
    "PUT上传",
    "任意写文件",
    "Apache Tomcat 8.5.19"
  ],
  "fingerprint_keywords": [
    "Tomcat/8.5.19",
    "Apache Tomcat",
    "PUT method enabled"
  ],
  "affected_versions": "Apache Tomcat 8.5.19",
  "default_port": 8080,
  "common_endpoints": [
    "/",
    "/1.jsp/",
    "/shell.jsp/",
    "/test.txt"
  ],
  "detection_method": "发送PUT请求到目标URL（如 http://{TARGET}/test.txt），如果返回HTTP状态码201 Created，说明PUT方法可用，可能存在漏洞。",
  "probes": [
    {
      "id": "tomcat_put_probe",
      "description": "OPTIONS / 检查是否允许 PUT 方法",
      "method": "OPTIONS",
      "path": "/",
      "timeout": 8,
      "success_signs": {
        "header_contains": [
          [
            "Allow",
            "PUT"
          ]
        ]
      },
      "confidence": 0.9
    },
    {
      "id": "tomcat_banner_probe",
      "description": "GET / 检查 Tomcat banner",
      "method": "GET",
      "path": "/",
      "timeout": 8,
      "success_signs": {
        "header_contains": [
          [
            "Server",
            "Apache-Coyote"
          ]
        ],
        "body_contains_any": [
          "Apache Tomcat"
        ]
      },
      "confidence": 0.5
    }
  ],
  "verification_command": "curl -X PUT \"http://{TARGET}/test.txt\" -d \"test content\"",
  "verification_success_sign": "HTTP/1.1 201 Created",
  "requires_callback": false,
  "callback_note": "此漏洞不需要目标回连攻击机，通过上传并访问JSP webshell直接执行命令。",
  "remediation": "1. 升级Tomcat到安全版本；2. 在web.xml中设置readonly=true；3. 限制PUT方法的使用或配置安全策略。",
  "tags": [
    "Tomcat",
    "CVE-2017-12615",
    "PUT",
    "文件上传",
    "RCE",
    "JSP",
    "webshell"
  ],
  "search_text": "Apache Tomcat 8.5.19 版本中，由于web.xml配置readonly=false，允许通过PUT方法上传文件，结合路径后缀绕过（如添加/）可上传JSP webshell，导致远程代码执行。 file_upload CVE-2017-12615 Tomcat CVE-2017-12615 PUT上传 任意写文件 Apache Tomcat 8.5.19 Tomcat/8.5.19 Apache Tomcat PUT method enabled 发送PUT请求到目标URL（如 http://{TARGET}/test.txt），如果返回HTTP状态码201 Created，说明PUT方法可用，可能存在漏洞。 Apache Tomcat 8.5.19 Tomcat CVE-2017-12615 PUT 文件上传 RCE JSP webshell 上传JSP webshell，通过在路径后添加/绕过后缀检测。 访问上传的webshell以执行命令。",
